{"key":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01|Mat|10","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","chapter":10,"textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024","parserRevision":"v11","verses":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":10,"verse":1,"text":"Summoning his twelve disciples, he gave them authority over unclean spirits, to drive them out and to heal every disease and sickness.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:2","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":10,"verse":2,"text":"These are the names of the twelve apostles: First, Simon, who is called Peter, and Andrew his brother; James the son of Zebedee, and John his brother;","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:3","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":10,"verse":3,"text":"Philip and Bartholomew; Thomas and Matthew the tax collector; James the son of Alphaeus, and Thaddaeus;","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:4","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":10,"verse":4,"text":"Simon the Zealot, and Judas Iscariot, who also betrayed him.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:5","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":10,"verse":5,"text":"Jesus sent out these twelve after giving them instructions: “Don’t take the road that leads to the Gentiles, and don’t enter any Samaritan town.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:6","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":10,"verse":6,"text":"Instead, go to the lost sheep of the house of Israel.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:7","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":10,"verse":7,"text":"As you go, proclaim, ‘The kingdom of heaven has come near.’","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:8","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":10,"verse":8,"text":"Heal the sick, raise the dead, cleanse those with leprosy, drive out demons. Freely you received, freely give.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:9","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":10,"verse":9,"text":"Don’t acquire gold, silver, or copper for your money-belts.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:10","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":10,"verse":10,"text":"Don’t take a traveling bag for the road, or an extra shirt, sandals, or a staff, for the worker is worthy of his food.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:11","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":10,"verse":11,"text":"When you enter any town or village, find out who is worthy, and stay there until you leave.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:12","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":10,"verse":12,"text":"Greet a household when you enter it,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:13","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":10,"verse":13,"text":"and if the household is worthy, let your peace be on it; but if it is unworthy, let your peace return to you.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:14","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":10,"verse":14,"text":"If anyone does not welcome you or listen to your words, shake the dust off your feet when you leave that house or town.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:15","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":10,"verse":15,"text":"Truly I tell you, it will be more tolerable on the day of judgment for the land of Sodom and Gomorrah than for that town.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:16","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":10,"verse":16,"text":"“Look, I’m sending you out like sheep among wolves. Therefore be as shrewd as serpents and as innocent as doves.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:17","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":10,"verse":17,"text":"Beware of them, because they will hand you over to local courts and flog you in their synagogues.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:18","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":10,"verse":18,"text":"You will even be brought before governors and kings because of me, to bear witness to them and to the Gentiles.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:19","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":10,"verse":19,"text":"But when they hand you over, don’t worry about how or what you are to speak. For you will be given what to say at that hour,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:20","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":10,"verse":20,"text":"because it isn’t you speaking, but the Spirit of your Father is speaking through you.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:21","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":10,"verse":21,"text":"“Brother will betray brother to death, and a father his child. Children will rise up against parents and have them put to death.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:22","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":10,"verse":22,"text":"You will be hated by everyone because of my name. But the one who endures to the end will be saved.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:23","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":10,"verse":23,"text":"When they persecute you in one town, flee to another. For truly I tell you, you will not have gone through the towns of Israel before the Son of Man comes.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:24","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":10,"verse":24,"text":"A disciple is not above his teacher, or a slave above his master.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:25","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":10,"verse":25,"text":"It is enough for a disciple to become like his teacher and a slave like his master. If they called the head of the house ‘Beelzebul,’ how much more the members of his household!","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:26","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":10,"verse":26,"text":"“Therefore, don’t be afraid of them, since there is nothing covered that won’t be uncovered and nothing hidden that won’t be made known.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:27","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":10,"verse":27,"text":"What I tell you in the dark, speak in the light. What you hear in a whisper, proclaim on the housetops.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:28","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":10,"verse":28,"text":"Don’t fear those who kill the body but are not able to kill the soul; rather, fear him who is able to destroy both soul and body in hell.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:29","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":10,"verse":29,"text":"Aren’t two sparrows sold for a penny? Yet not one of them falls to the ground without your Father’s consent.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:30","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":10,"verse":30,"text":"But even the hairs of your head have all been counted.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:31","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":10,"verse":31,"text":"So don’t be afraid; you are worth more than many sparrows.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:32","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":10,"verse":32,"text":"“Therefore, everyone who will acknowledge me before others, I will also acknowledge him before my Father in heaven.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:33","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":10,"verse":33,"text":"But whoever denies me before others, I will also deny him before my Father in heaven.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:34","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":10,"verse":34,"text":"Don’t assume that I came to bring peace on the earth. I did not come to bring peace, but a sword.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:35","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":10,"verse":35,"text":"For I came to turn","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:36","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":10,"verse":36,"text":"and a man’s enemies will be","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:37","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":10,"verse":37,"text":"The one who loves a father or mother more than me is not worthy of me; the one who loves a son or daughter more than me is not worthy of me.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:38","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":10,"verse":38,"text":"And whoever doesn’t take up his cross and follow me is not worthy of me.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:39","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":10,"verse":39,"text":"Anyone who finds his life will lose it, and anyone who loses his life because of me will find it.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:40","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":10,"verse":40,"text":"“The one who welcomes you welcomes me, and the one who welcomes me welcomes him who sent me.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:41","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":10,"verse":41,"text":"Anyone who welcomes a prophet because he is a prophet will receive a prophet’s reward. And anyone who welcomes a righteous person because he’s righteous will receive a righteous person’s reward.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:42","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":10,"verse":42,"text":"And whoever gives even a cup of cold water to one of these little ones because he is a disciple, truly I tell you, he will never lose his reward.”","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"}],"layout":{"bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","chapter":10,"paragraphStarts":[1,5,16,21,26,32,36,37,40],"headings":[{"beforeVerse":1,"text":"Commissioning the Twelve"},{"beforeVerse":16,"text":"Persecutions Predicted"},{"beforeVerse":26,"text":"Fear God"},{"beforeVerse":32,"text":"Acknowledging Christ"},{"beforeVerse":40,"text":"A Cup of Cold Water"}],"poetryBlocks":[],"studyByVerse":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:1","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Summoning his twelve disciples, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 3:13–19","book":"Mrk","chapter":3,"verse":13,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 6:13–16","book":"Mrk","chapter":6,"verse":13,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" he gave them authority over unclean spirits, to drive them out and to heal every "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or every kind of"},{"kind":"text","text":" disease and sickness. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Or physical ailment"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 9:35","book":"Mat","chapter":9,"verse":35,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 6:7","book":"Mrk","chapter":6,"verse":7,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 9:1","book":"Luk","chapter":9,"verse":1,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mk 3:13–19","book":"Mrk","chapter":3,"verse":13},{"label":"Mk 6:13–16","book":"Mrk","chapter":6,"verse":13},{"label":"Mt 9:35","book":"Mat","chapter":9,"verse":35},{"label":"Mk 6:7","book":"Mrk","chapter":6,"verse":7},{"label":"Lk 9:1","book":"Luk","chapter":9,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or every kind of"},{"marker":2,"text":"Or physical ailment"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:2","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"These are the names of the twelve apostles: "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 4:18","book":"Mat","chapter":4,"verse":18,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 4:21","book":"Mat","chapter":4,"verse":21,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 16:18","book":"Mat","chapter":16,"verse":18,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 1:42","book":"Jhn","chapter":1,"verse":42,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" First, Simon, who is called Peter, and Andrew his brother; James the son of Zebedee, and John his brother; "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 4:18","book":"Mat","chapter":4,"verse":18},{"label":"Mt 4:21","book":"Mat","chapter":4,"verse":21},{"label":"Mt 16:18","book":"Mat","chapter":16,"verse":18},{"label":"Jn 1:42","book":"Jhn","chapter":1,"verse":42}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:3","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Philip and Bartholomew; Thomas and Matthew the tax collector; James the son of Alphaeus, and Thaddaeus; "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":3,"text":"Other mss read and Lebbaeus, whose surname was Thaddaeus"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":3,"text":"Other mss read and Lebbaeus, whose surname was Thaddaeus"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:4","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Simon the Zealot, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":4,"text":"Lit the Cananaean"},{"kind":"text","text":" and Judas Iscariot, who also betrayed him. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 26:14","book":"Mat","chapter":26,"verse":14,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 22:3","book":"Luk","chapter":22,"verse":3,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 6:71","book":"Jhn","chapter":6,"verse":71,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 13:2","book":"Jhn","chapter":13,"verse":2,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 13:26","book":"Jhn","chapter":13,"verse":26,"letter":"e"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 26:14","book":"Mat","chapter":26,"verse":14},{"label":"Lk 22:3","book":"Luk","chapter":22,"verse":3},{"label":"Jn 6:71","book":"Jhn","chapter":6,"verse":71},{"label":"Jn 13:2","book":"Jhn","chapter":13,"verse":2},{"label":"Jn 13:26","book":"Jhn","chapter":13,"verse":26}],"footnotes":[{"marker":4,"text":"Lit the Cananaean"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:5","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Jesus sent out these twelve after giving them instructions: “Don’t take the road that leads to the Gentiles, and don’t enter any Samaritan"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Kg 17:24","book":"2Ki","chapter":17,"verse":24,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 9:52","book":"Luk","chapter":9,"verse":52,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 17:16","book":"Luk","chapter":17,"verse":16,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 4:9","book":"Jhn","chapter":4,"verse":9,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 8:25","book":"Act","chapter":8,"verse":25,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" town. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"2Kg 17:24","book":"2Ki","chapter":17,"verse":24},{"label":"Lk 9:52","book":"Luk","chapter":9,"verse":52},{"label":"Lk 17:16","book":"Luk","chapter":17,"verse":16},{"label":"Jn 4:9","book":"Jhn","chapter":4,"verse":9},{"label":"Ac 8:25","book":"Act","chapter":8,"verse":25}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:6","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Instead, go to the lost sheep"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 119:36","book":"Psa","chapter":119,"verse":36,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 53:6","book":"Isa","chapter":53,"verse":6,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 50:6","book":"Jer","chapter":50,"verse":6,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 9:36","book":"Mat","chapter":9,"verse":36,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 18:12","book":"Mat","chapter":18,"verse":12,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" of the house of Israel."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 2:36","book":"Act","chapter":2,"verse":36,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 7:42","book":"Act","chapter":7,"verse":42,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 8:8","book":"Heb","chapter":8,"verse":8,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 8:10","book":"Heb","chapter":8,"verse":10,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ps 119:36","book":"Psa","chapter":119,"verse":36},{"label":"Is 53:6","book":"Isa","chapter":53,"verse":6},{"label":"Jr 50:6","book":"Jer","chapter":50,"verse":6},{"label":"Mt 9:36","book":"Mat","chapter":9,"verse":36},{"label":"Mt 18:12","book":"Mat","chapter":18,"verse":12},{"label":"Ac 2:36","book":"Act","chapter":2,"verse":36},{"label":"Ac 7:42","book":"Act","chapter":7,"verse":42},{"label":"Heb 8:8","book":"Heb","chapter":8,"verse":8},{"label":"Heb 8:10","book":"Heb","chapter":8,"verse":10}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:7","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"As you go, proclaim, ‘The kingdom of heaven has come near.’"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 3:2–3","book":"Mat","chapter":3,"verse":2,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 4:17","book":"Mat","chapter":4,"verse":17,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 10:9","book":"Luk","chapter":10,"verse":9,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 3:2–3","book":"Mat","chapter":3,"verse":2},{"label":"Mt 4:17","book":"Mat","chapter":4,"verse":17},{"label":"Lk 10:9","book":"Luk","chapter":10,"verse":9}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:8","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Heal the sick, raise the dead, cleanse those with leprosy,"},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Gk lepros; a term for various skin diseases; see Lv 13–14"},{"kind":"text","text":" drive out demons."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 3:15","book":"Mrk","chapter":3,"verse":15,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 9:20","book":"Rev","chapter":9,"verse":20,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 18:2","book":"Rev","chapter":18,"verse":2,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" Freely you received, freely give. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mk 3:15","book":"Mrk","chapter":3,"verse":15},{"label":"Rv 9:20","book":"Rev","chapter":9,"verse":20},{"label":"Rv 18:2","book":"Rev","chapter":18,"verse":2}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Gk lepros; a term for various skin diseases; see Lv 13–14"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:9","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Don’t acquire gold, silver, or copper for your money-belts."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 6:6–8","book":"Mrk","chapter":6,"verse":6,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 9:3–5","book":"Luk","chapter":9,"verse":3,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 10:4–12","book":"Luk","chapter":10,"verse":4,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mk 6:6–8","book":"Mrk","chapter":6,"verse":6},{"label":"Lk 9:3–5","book":"Luk","chapter":9,"verse":3},{"label":"Lk 10:4–12","book":"Luk","chapter":10,"verse":4}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:10","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Don’t take a traveling bag for the road, or an extra shirt, sandals, or a staff, for the worker"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 10:7","book":"Luk","chapter":10,"verse":7,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 9:14","book":"1Co","chapter":9,"verse":14,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Tm 5:18","book":"1Ti","chapter":5,"verse":18,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" is worthy of his food. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lk 10:7","book":"Luk","chapter":10,"verse":7},{"label":"1Co 9:14","book":"1Co","chapter":9,"verse":14},{"label":"1Tm 5:18","book":"1Ti","chapter":5,"verse":18}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"When you enter any town or village, find out who is worthy, and stay there until you leave. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Greet a household when you enter it,"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Sm 25:6","book":"1Sa","chapter":25,"verse":6,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Ch 12:18","book":"1Ch","chapter":12,"verse":18,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 122:7–8","book":"Psa","chapter":122,"verse":7,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Sm 25:6","book":"1Sa","chapter":25,"verse":6},{"label":"1Ch 12:18","book":"1Ch","chapter":12,"verse":18},{"label":"Ps 122:7–8","book":"Psa","chapter":122,"verse":7}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"and if the household is worthy, let your peace be on it; but if it is unworthy, let your peace return to you."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 35:13","book":"Psa","chapter":35,"verse":13,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 8:8","book":"Mat","chapter":8,"verse":8,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 16:15","book":"Act","chapter":16,"verse":15,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ps 35:13","book":"Psa","chapter":35,"verse":13},{"label":"Mt 8:8","book":"Mat","chapter":8,"verse":8},{"label":"Ac 16:15","book":"Act","chapter":16,"verse":15}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"If anyone does not welcome you or listen to your words, shake the dust off your feet"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Neh 5:13","book":"Neh","chapter":5,"verse":13,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 10:11","book":"Luk","chapter":10,"verse":11,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 13:51","book":"Act","chapter":13,"verse":51,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" when you leave that house or town. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Neh 5:13","book":"Neh","chapter":5,"verse":13},{"label":"Lk 10:11","book":"Luk","chapter":10,"verse":11},{"label":"Ac 13:51","book":"Act","chapter":13,"verse":51}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Truly I tell you, it will be more tolerable on the day of judgment"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 12:36","book":"Mat","chapter":12,"verse":36,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 17:31","book":"Act","chapter":17,"verse":31,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 10:25","book":"Heb","chapter":10,"verse":25,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Pt 2:9","book":"2Pe","chapter":2,"verse":9,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Jn 4:17","book":"1Jn","chapter":4,"verse":17,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" for the land of Sodom and Gomorrah than for that town."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 11:22","book":"Mat","chapter":11,"verse":22,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 11:24","book":"Mat","chapter":11,"verse":24,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Pt 2:6","book":"2Pe","chapter":2,"verse":6,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jd 1:6","book":"Jud","chapter":1,"verse":6,"letter":"i"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 12:36","book":"Mat","chapter":12,"verse":36},{"label":"Ac 17:31","book":"Act","chapter":17,"verse":31},{"label":"Heb 10:25","book":"Heb","chapter":10,"verse":25},{"label":"2Pt 2:9","book":"2Pe","chapter":2,"verse":9},{"label":"1Jn 4:17","book":"1Jn","chapter":4,"verse":17},{"label":"Mt 11:22","book":"Mat","chapter":11,"verse":22},{"label":"Mt 11:24","book":"Mat","chapter":11,"verse":24},{"label":"2Pt 2:6","book":"2Pe","chapter":2,"verse":6},{"label":"Jd 1:6","book":"Jud","chapter":1,"verse":6}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Look, I’m sending you out like sheep among wolves. Therefore be as shrewd as serpents and as innocent as doves."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 3:1","book":"Gen","chapter":3,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 10:3","book":"Luk","chapter":10,"verse":3,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 16:19","book":"Rom","chapter":16,"verse":19,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 2:15","book":"Php","chapter":2,"verse":15,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gn 3:1","book":"Gen","chapter":3,"verse":1},{"label":"Lk 10:3","book":"Luk","chapter":10,"verse":3},{"label":"Rm 16:19","book":"Rom","chapter":16,"verse":19},{"label":"Php 2:15","book":"Php","chapter":2,"verse":15}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Beware of them, because they will hand you over to local courts"},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or sanhedrins"},{"kind":"text","text":" and flog you in their synagogues."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 13:9","book":"Mrk","chapter":13,"verse":9,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 13:11","book":"Mrk","chapter":13,"verse":11,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 12:11–12","book":"Luk","chapter":12,"verse":11,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 5:40","book":"Act","chapter":5,"verse":40,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 26:11","book":"Act","chapter":26,"verse":11,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mk 13:9","book":"Mrk","chapter":13,"verse":9},{"label":"Mk 13:11","book":"Mrk","chapter":13,"verse":11},{"label":"Lk 12:11–12","book":"Luk","chapter":12,"verse":11},{"label":"Ac 5:40","book":"Act","chapter":5,"verse":40},{"label":"Ac 26:11","book":"Act","chapter":26,"verse":11}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or sanhedrins"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"You will even be brought before governors and kings because of me, to bear witness to them and to the Gentiles."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 28:19","book":"Mat","chapter":28,"verse":19,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 1:5","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":5,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 1:16","book":"Gal","chapter":1,"verse":16,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 28:19","book":"Mat","chapter":28,"verse":19},{"label":"Rm 1:5","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":5},{"label":"Gl 1:16","book":"Gal","chapter":1,"verse":16}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But when they hand you over, don’t worry about how or what you are to speak."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 4:12","book":"Exo","chapter":4,"verse":12,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 23:5","book":"Num","chapter":23,"verse":5,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 18:18","book":"Deu","chapter":18,"verse":18,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 6:25","book":"Mat","chapter":6,"verse":25,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" For you will be given what to say at that hour, "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 4:12","book":"Exo","chapter":4,"verse":12},{"label":"Nm 23:5","book":"Num","chapter":23,"verse":5},{"label":"Dt 18:18","book":"Deu","chapter":18,"verse":18},{"label":"Mt 6:25","book":"Mat","chapter":6,"verse":25}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:20","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"because it isn’t you speaking, but the Spirit"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 51:11","book":"Psa","chapter":51,"verse":11,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 1:33","book":"Jhn","chapter":1,"verse":33,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 2:4","book":"Act","chapter":2,"verse":4,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 8:9","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":9,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 5:25","book":"Gal","chapter":5,"verse":25,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ti 3:5","book":"Tit","chapter":3,"verse":5,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" of your Father is speaking through you."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 12:12","book":"Luk","chapter":12,"verse":12,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 4:8","book":"Act","chapter":4,"verse":8,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 13:9","book":"Act","chapter":13,"verse":9,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 13:3","book":"2Co","chapter":13,"verse":3,"letter":"j"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ps 51:11","book":"Psa","chapter":51,"verse":11},{"label":"Jn 1:33","book":"Jhn","chapter":1,"verse":33},{"label":"Ac 2:4","book":"Act","chapter":2,"verse":4},{"label":"Rm 8:9","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":9},{"label":"Gl 5:25","book":"Gal","chapter":5,"verse":25},{"label":"Ti 3:5","book":"Tit","chapter":3,"verse":5},{"label":"Lk 12:12","book":"Luk","chapter":12,"verse":12},{"label":"Ac 4:8","book":"Act","chapter":4,"verse":8},{"label":"Ac 13:9","book":"Act","chapter":13,"verse":9},{"label":"2Co 13:3","book":"2Co","chapter":13,"verse":3}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:21","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Brother will betray brother to death, and a father his child. Children will rise up against parents and have them put to death."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mc 7:6","book":"Mic","chapter":7,"verse":6,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 10:35–36","book":"Mat","chapter":10,"verse":35,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 13:12","book":"Mrk","chapter":13,"verse":12,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mc 7:6","book":"Mic","chapter":7,"verse":6},{"label":"Mt 10:35–36","book":"Mat","chapter":10,"verse":35},{"label":"Mk 13:12","book":"Mrk","chapter":13,"verse":12}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:22","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"You will be hated by everyone because of my name."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 24:9","book":"Mat","chapter":24,"verse":9,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 21:17","book":"Luk","chapter":21,"verse":17,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 15:18","book":"Jhn","chapter":15,"verse":18,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" But the one who endures to the end will be saved."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 24:13","book":"Mat","chapter":24,"verse":13,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 13:13","book":"Mrk","chapter":13,"verse":13,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 12:12–13","book":"Jhn","chapter":12,"verse":12,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 24:9","book":"Mat","chapter":24,"verse":9},{"label":"Lk 21:17","book":"Luk","chapter":21,"verse":17},{"label":"Jn 15:18","book":"Jhn","chapter":15,"verse":18},{"label":"Mt 24:13","book":"Mat","chapter":24,"verse":13},{"label":"Mk 13:13","book":"Mrk","chapter":13,"verse":13},{"label":"Jn 12:12–13","book":"Jhn","chapter":12,"verse":12}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:23","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"When they persecute you in one town, flee to another."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 12:15","book":"Mat","chapter":12,"verse":15,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 8:1","book":"Act","chapter":8,"verse":1,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 9:25","book":"Act","chapter":9,"verse":25,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 14:6","book":"Act","chapter":14,"verse":6,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 17:10","book":"Act","chapter":17,"verse":10,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" For truly I tell you, you will not have gone through the towns of Israel before the Son of Man comes. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 12:15","book":"Mat","chapter":12,"verse":15},{"label":"Ac 8:1","book":"Act","chapter":8,"verse":1},{"label":"Ac 9:25","book":"Act","chapter":9,"verse":25},{"label":"Ac 14:6","book":"Act","chapter":14,"verse":6},{"label":"Ac 17:10","book":"Act","chapter":17,"verse":10}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:24","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"A disciple"},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or student"},{"kind":"text","text":" is not above his teacher, or a slave above his master."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 6:40","book":"Luk","chapter":6,"verse":40,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 13:16","book":"Jhn","chapter":13,"verse":16,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 15:20","book":"Jhn","chapter":15,"verse":20,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lk 6:40","book":"Luk","chapter":6,"verse":40},{"label":"Jn 13:16","book":"Jhn","chapter":13,"verse":16},{"label":"Jn 15:20","book":"Jhn","chapter":15,"verse":20}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or student"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:25","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"It is enough for a disciple to become like his teacher and a slave like his master. If they called the head of the house ‘Beelzebul,’ how much more the members of his household!"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Kg 1:2","book":"2Ki","chapter":1,"verse":2,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 12:24","book":"Mat","chapter":12,"verse":24,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 12:27","book":"Mat","chapter":12,"verse":27,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 3:22","book":"Mrk","chapter":3,"verse":22,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 11:15","book":"Luk","chapter":11,"verse":15,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 11:18","book":"Luk","chapter":11,"verse":18,"letter":"f"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"2Kg 1:2","book":"2Ki","chapter":1,"verse":2},{"label":"Mt 12:24","book":"Mat","chapter":12,"verse":24},{"label":"Mt 12:27","book":"Mat","chapter":12,"verse":27},{"label":"Mk 3:22","book":"Mrk","chapter":3,"verse":22},{"label":"Lk 11:15","book":"Luk","chapter":11,"verse":15},{"label":"Lk 11:18","book":"Luk","chapter":11,"verse":18}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:26","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Therefore,"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 12:2–9","book":"Luk","chapter":12,"verse":2,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" don’t be afraid of them, since there is nothing covered that won’t be uncovered and nothing hidden that won’t be made known."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 4:22","book":"Mrk","chapter":4,"verse":22,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 8:17","book":"Luk","chapter":8,"verse":17,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 12:2","book":"Luk","chapter":12,"verse":2,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lk 12:2–9","book":"Luk","chapter":12,"verse":2},{"label":"Mk 4:22","book":"Mrk","chapter":4,"verse":22},{"label":"Lk 8:17","book":"Luk","chapter":8,"verse":17},{"label":"Lk 12:2","book":"Luk","chapter":12,"verse":2}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:27","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"What I tell you in the dark, speak in the light. What you hear in a whisper,"},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit in the ear"},{"kind":"text","text":" proclaim on the housetops."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 24:17","book":"Mat","chapter":24,"verse":17,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 5:19","book":"Luk","chapter":5,"verse":19,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 12:3","book":"Luk","chapter":12,"verse":3,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 5:20","book":"Act","chapter":5,"verse":20,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 24:17","book":"Mat","chapter":24,"verse":17},{"label":"Lk 5:19","book":"Luk","chapter":5,"verse":19},{"label":"Lk 12:3","book":"Luk","chapter":12,"verse":3},{"label":"Ac 5:20","book":"Act","chapter":5,"verse":20}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit in the ear"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:28","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Don’t fear those who kill the body but are not able to kill the soul;"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 8:12–13","book":"Isa","chapter":8,"verse":12,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 51:12–13","book":"Isa","chapter":51,"verse":12,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 1:8","book":"Jer","chapter":1,"verse":8,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 3:14","book":"1Pe","chapter":3,"verse":14,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" rather, fear him who is able to destroy both soul and body in hell."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 5:22","book":"Mat","chapter":5,"verse":22,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 12:5","book":"Luk","chapter":12,"verse":5,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 10:31","book":"Heb","chapter":10,"verse":31,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jms 4:12","book":"Jas","chapter":4,"verse":12,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Is 8:12–13","book":"Isa","chapter":8,"verse":12},{"label":"Is 51:12–13","book":"Isa","chapter":51,"verse":12},{"label":"Jr 1:8","book":"Jer","chapter":1,"verse":8},{"label":"1Pt 3:14","book":"1Pe","chapter":3,"verse":14},{"label":"Mt 5:22","book":"Mat","chapter":5,"verse":22},{"label":"Lk 12:5","book":"Luk","chapter":12,"verse":5},{"label":"Heb 10:31","book":"Heb","chapter":10,"verse":31},{"label":"Jms 4:12","book":"Jas","chapter":4,"verse":12}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:29","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Aren’t two sparrows sold for a penny?"},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Gk assarion, a small copper coin"},{"kind":"text","text":" Yet not one of them falls to the ground without your Father’s"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 5:16","book":"Mat","chapter":5,"verse":16,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 11:27","book":"Mat","chapter":11,"verse":27,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 11:13","book":"Luk","chapter":11,"verse":13,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 8:42","book":"Jhn","chapter":8,"verse":42,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" consent."},{"kind":"footnote","marker":3,"text":"Lit ground apart from your Father"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 5:16","book":"Mat","chapter":5,"verse":16},{"label":"Mt 11:27","book":"Mat","chapter":11,"verse":27},{"label":"Lk 11:13","book":"Luk","chapter":11,"verse":13},{"label":"Jn 8:42","book":"Jhn","chapter":8,"verse":42}],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"text":"Gk assarion, a small copper coin"},{"marker":3,"text":"Lit ground apart from your Father"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:30","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But even the hairs of your head have all been counted."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Sm 14:45","book":"1Sa","chapter":14,"verse":45,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Sm 14:11","book":"2Sa","chapter":14,"verse":11,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 21:18","book":"Luk","chapter":21,"verse":18,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 27:34","book":"Act","chapter":27,"verse":34,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Sm 14:45","book":"1Sa","chapter":14,"verse":45},{"label":"2Sm 14:11","book":"2Sa","chapter":14,"verse":11},{"label":"Lk 21:18","book":"Luk","chapter":21,"verse":18},{"label":"Ac 27:34","book":"Act","chapter":27,"verse":34}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:31","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"So don’t be afraid; you are worth more than many sparrows."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 6:26","book":"Mat","chapter":6,"verse":26,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 12:12","book":"Mat","chapter":12,"verse":12,"letter":"b"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 6:26","book":"Mat","chapter":6,"verse":26},{"label":"Mt 12:12","book":"Mat","chapter":12,"verse":12}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:32","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Therefore, everyone who will acknowledge me before others, I will also acknowledge him before my Father in heaven."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 12:8","book":"Luk","chapter":12,"verse":8,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 10:9–10","book":"Rom","chapter":10,"verse":9,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 3:5","book":"Rev","chapter":3,"verse":5,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lk 12:8","book":"Luk","chapter":12,"verse":8},{"label":"Rm 10:9–10","book":"Rom","chapter":10,"verse":9},{"label":"Rv 3:5","book":"Rev","chapter":3,"verse":5}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:33","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But whoever denies me before others,"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 8:38","book":"Mrk","chapter":8,"verse":38,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 9:26","book":"Luk","chapter":9,"verse":26,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Tm 2:12","book":"2Ti","chapter":2,"verse":12,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Pt 2:1","book":"2Pe","chapter":2,"verse":1,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" I will also deny him before my Father in heaven. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mk 8:38","book":"Mrk","chapter":8,"verse":38},{"label":"Lk 9:26","book":"Luk","chapter":9,"verse":26},{"label":"2Tm 2:12","book":"2Ti","chapter":2,"verse":12},{"label":"2Pt 2:1","book":"2Pe","chapter":2,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:34","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Don’t assume that I came to bring peace on the earth. I did not come to bring peace, but a sword."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 12:51–53","book":"Luk","chapter":12,"verse":51,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lk 12:51–53","book":"Luk","chapter":12,"verse":51}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:35","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For I came to turn"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:36","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"and a man’s enemies will be"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:37","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The one who loves a father or mother more than me is not worthy of me;"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 14:25–27","book":"Luk","chapter":14,"verse":25,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" the one who loves a son or daughter more than me is not worthy of me. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lk 14:25–27","book":"Luk","chapter":14,"verse":25}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:38","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"And whoever doesn’t take up his cross and follow me is not worthy of me. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:39","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Anyone who finds his life will lose it,"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 16:25","book":"Mat","chapter":16,"verse":25,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 8:35","book":"Mrk","chapter":8,"verse":35,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 9:24","book":"Luk","chapter":9,"verse":24,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 17:33","book":"Luk","chapter":17,"verse":33,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 12:25","book":"Jhn","chapter":12,"verse":25,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" and anyone who loses his life because of me will find it."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 9:9","book":"Mat","chapter":9,"verse":9,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 8:12","book":"Jhn","chapter":8,"verse":12,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 12:26","book":"Jhn","chapter":12,"verse":26,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 21:19","book":"Jhn","chapter":21,"verse":19,"letter":"i"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 16:25","book":"Mat","chapter":16,"verse":25},{"label":"Mk 8:35","book":"Mrk","chapter":8,"verse":35},{"label":"Lk 9:24","book":"Luk","chapter":9,"verse":24},{"label":"Lk 17:33","book":"Luk","chapter":17,"verse":33},{"label":"Jn 12:25","book":"Jhn","chapter":12,"verse":25},{"label":"Mt 9:9","book":"Mat","chapter":9,"verse":9},{"label":"Jn 8:12","book":"Jhn","chapter":8,"verse":12},{"label":"Jn 12:26","book":"Jhn","chapter":12,"verse":26},{"label":"Jn 21:19","book":"Jhn","chapter":21,"verse":19}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:40","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“The one who welcomes you welcomes me,"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 18:5","book":"Mat","chapter":18,"verse":5,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 10:16","book":"Luk","chapter":10,"verse":16,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 13:20","book":"Jhn","chapter":13,"verse":20,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 4:14","book":"Gal","chapter":4,"verse":14,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" and the one who welcomes me welcomes him who sent me."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 9:37","book":"Mrk","chapter":9,"verse":37,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 9:48","book":"Luk","chapter":9,"verse":48,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 12:44","book":"Jhn","chapter":12,"verse":44,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 18:5","book":"Mat","chapter":18,"verse":5},{"label":"Lk 10:16","book":"Luk","chapter":10,"verse":16},{"label":"Jn 13:20","book":"Jhn","chapter":13,"verse":20},{"label":"Gl 4:14","book":"Gal","chapter":4,"verse":14},{"label":"Mk 9:37","book":"Mrk","chapter":9,"verse":37},{"label":"Lk 9:48","book":"Luk","chapter":9,"verse":48},{"label":"Jn 12:44","book":"Jhn","chapter":12,"verse":44}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:41","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Anyone who welcomes a prophet"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Kg 17:10","book":"1Ki","chapter":17,"verse":10,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Kg 18:4","book":"1Ki","chapter":18,"verse":4,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Kg 4:8","book":"2Ki","chapter":4,"verse":8,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"3Jn 5–8","book":"3Jn","chapter":1,"verse":5,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" because he is a prophet"},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit prophet in the name of a prophet"},{"kind":"text","text":" will receive a prophet’s reward. And anyone who welcomes a righteous person because he’s righteous"},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Lit person in the name of a righteous person"},{"kind":"text","text":" will receive a righteous person’s reward. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Kg 17:10","book":"1Ki","chapter":17,"verse":10},{"label":"1Kg 18:4","book":"1Ki","chapter":18,"verse":4},{"label":"2Kg 4:8","book":"2Ki","chapter":4,"verse":8},{"label":"3Jn 5–8","book":"3Jn","chapter":1,"verse":5}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit prophet in the name of a prophet"},{"marker":2,"text":"Lit person in the name of a righteous person"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:10:42","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"And whoever gives"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 25:40","book":"Mat","chapter":25,"verse":40,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 9:41","book":"Mrk","chapter":9,"verse":41,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 6:10","book":"Heb","chapter":6,"verse":10,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" even a cup of cold water to one of these little ones because he is a disciple,"},{"kind":"footnote","marker":3,"text":"Lit little ones in the name of a disciple"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 28:19","book":"Mat","chapter":28,"verse":19,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 14:26","book":"Luk","chapter":14,"verse":26,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 8:31","book":"Jhn","chapter":8,"verse":31,"letter":"f"},{"